Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.52,0:00:06.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,離開這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:10.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,村裡的人還在懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊是不是還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:14.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:22.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是作為祭品才來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:24.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為了平息夜禍作亂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.25,0:00:29.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,當然 現在我和姊姊都不會相信那種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:30.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:32.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我一直都一個人 所以沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就算依人和蒼乃不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說我們不在了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.21,0:00:52.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,三個人一起離開這裡吧 可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,三個人 一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:56.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:58.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天和姊姊談過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:02.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,即使離開這裡 也要和茉莉一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不要再說那樣的話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:08.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:17.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:22.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一…二~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉突然來訪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:24.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想再一次好好和你談談
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,選擇離開這裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:35.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人選擇了我 說要和我一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:39.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,聽依人說了 他要讓你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:47.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真不錯 果然依人最先考慮的還是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:52.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不想讓你悲傷 不想讓你痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:54.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直都只考慮這些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:57.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我已經忍受不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:01.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜歡依人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,與依人邂逅 一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣之後 果然不想分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得一個人很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.94,0:04:12.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把依人給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:16.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你認真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我已經得到依人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.49,0:04:22.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人現在在我這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:23.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們來決定誰能留在依人的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我買了爆米花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你連這個都準備了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是真的要放映什麼電影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,需要氣氛 氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 那個人會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:24.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:27.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,主人公最後一定會得到幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:29.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,臉被劈成兩半了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:33.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是恐怖電影的設定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,果然約會看電影的話應該看恐怖的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:37.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我不怎麼喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:41.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:42.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:47.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啦 那下次試試看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:55.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候去看一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:01.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:04.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想她應該會來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:06.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我說得有點過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:07.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 該抱歉的人應該是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我和蒼乃之間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:16.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,被捲進來的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個穿運動服的傢伙有點可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看 行動起來很不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:24.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:28.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 那個腳上的污痕是剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 那對情侶被襲擊地方的泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像電影的類型變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 原本是恐怖類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:39.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:45.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡是一種什麼樣的感覺呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:50.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢 雖然一直都活著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:53.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有對這件事一無所知呢 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:06:58.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？ 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是空地嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:07.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:30.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 你在吧 依人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我們戰鬥也毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:38.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,即使把我打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我失去了夜禍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人就無法活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:45.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:46.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:51.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把你打倒 然後讓可憐的依人消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:55.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:20.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:24.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊沒必要去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣做的話 大家會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:33.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我成為夜禍的祭品後 大家會幸福的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.74,0:08:34.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:51.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:57.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 太好了 你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.39,0:08:59.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 她就是夜禍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.03,0:09:23.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是我 是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:28.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就因為身為祭品的我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:57.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把依人還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:09:59.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:00.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的依人已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:04.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:07.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的依人在那個時候已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他不可以待在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我在那個時候也應該死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和依人一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,變成現在這樣不就是因為你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:22.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,根本沒有叫你來幫我 你卻… 你卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 所以我要把一切恢復到原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:10:59.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:08.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了不是一個人時是什麼感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,知道有人在身邊時的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:28.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:40.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.77,0:11:49.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到的只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以把死掉的人變成夜禍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:54.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:56.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我找過了 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:01.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:05.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼讓我活過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:09.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想繼續活在沒有依人的世界裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:30.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 不要走 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:38.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:12.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:42.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:48.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:50.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:55.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能跟姊姊一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:02.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉要讓你消失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是我拜託她的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我… 不是依人 什麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我本是不該留在這裡的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.58,0:14:21.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我要回到我原本的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和姊姊一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:26.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:29.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我消失了 依人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就什麼都不會留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡消失的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就會好像什麼都沒有發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:36.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那才是正確的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一開始我就不會做那樣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 有了夜禍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:43.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想就可以做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:48.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想又可以和依人在一起生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.59,0:14:53.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說這都是沒有意義的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:55.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我悲傷痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,終於找到的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說是沒有意義的嗎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:00.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:01.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:19.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我要快點去依人那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多已經開始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:38.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:42.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你說想要喝果汁 我們才下來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下一班車呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.17,0:15:47.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只有等頭班車了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:49.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:51.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:53.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:05.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為茉莉已經下定決心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是沒有任何動搖和猶豫的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,幫助也好 擔心也好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:14.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她能做到 不管多麼困難的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:20.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.55,0:16:28.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是那兩個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:43.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,結束後馬上就放你下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:50.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就算茉莉不在的話 我也不會跟姊姊走的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:53.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,強行也要把你帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.40,0:16:55.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是姊姊的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:56.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:58.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我是姐姐製造的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:05.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是真正的依人 你就不會這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.24,0:17:07.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的依人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,做了讓姊姊感到不安的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也做過姊姊不希望他做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但那就是活著的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有不如意的事 也有討厭的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是阻止不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我的話可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:25.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦出事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:26.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以失去記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,當作什麼都沒有發生過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:29.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:30.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為如此我才覺得很空虛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:34.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:36.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是依人 我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:41.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:44.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:58.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.14,0:18:03.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我們做個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:08.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 正如我意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:20.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:35.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.23,0:19:39.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等著我 馬上就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:54.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:20:00.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,讓這一切都結束吧 姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:01.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:13.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:15.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 放開我 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:44.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:46.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,藍色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.14,0:20:47.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:05.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,往那把刀裡傾注你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,轉移到夜禍人體內
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:09.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以變回人類
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把蒼乃變回人類
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:51.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就可以變回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:54.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:58.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:33.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,飛向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:34.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,飛過天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:37.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,想證實自己並非一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道漂浮的雲朵的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:43.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,比任何人都虔誠地一直在祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:45.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空
